strings.Value: "The way you finished off those trolls was spectacular! You really have what it takes to be a hero just like in the stories. I feel like we are making a difference, just like Guy and the Archknights of Avistan. You sort of remind me of him a little..."
"I did what I had to. They broke the law and now they have paid the price. Here in this wild land, it is as close to justice as we are likely to see. And that is fine by me."
